Name: Kohler's disease
Definition: An osteochondrosis that results_in death and collapse located_in navicular bone of foot.

Name: Scheuermann's disease
Definition: An osteochondrosis that results_in abnormal bone growth and curvature located_in thoracic vertebral column.

Name: obsolete anterior nasal diphtheria
Definition: A diphtheria that is characterized by a mucopurulent nasal discharge (containing both mucus and pus) which may become blood-tinged. A white membrane usually forms on the nasal septum. The disease is usually fairly mild because of apparent poor systemic absorption of toxin in this location

Name: Legg-Calve-Perthes disease
Definition: An osteochondrosis that results_in death and fracture located_in hip joint.
